      <title>婴儿配方奶粉成本飙升给大品牌带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/baby-formula-from-nestle-danone-and-others-investigated-over-pricing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有关襁褓和液体便便的帖子之间，Mumsnet 和 Reddit 等在线论坛上充斥着焦虑、睡眠不足的父母，他们在寻找购买哪种婴儿配方奶粉的建议。随着配方奶粉成本持续攀升——现在在英国一个月的费用约为 89 英镑（112 美元）——护理人员的压力只会越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/baby-formula-from-nestle-danone-and-others-investigated-over-pricing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
